snippet.title: Ash of Legends: Gameplay Trailer #2
snippet.description:
Ash of Legends is a VR 1st-person tower defense, Where you build, shoot, and grapple in and out of various terrain. Slash and mow them down with over a dozen weapons. Play as a Soldier or Strategist with two unique playstyles. Build your defense or Shoot them down anything to protect the cache from the hordes of enemies. Now rise to the top and Be a Legend.
